      "description": "This panel shows the 95th percentile latency for complete admission requests processed by Kyverno, meaning 95% of admission requests are completed within this time or faster. Only 5% take longer than the displayed value.\n\nKey Difference from Policy Rule Latency:\n• Policy Rule Latency: Measures execution time for individual policy rules (micro-level)\n  - Example: How long does the \"disallow-privileged\" rule take to execute? (1-5ms)\n• Admission Request Latency: Measures total time for entire admission requests (macro-level)  \n  - Example: How long does it take to validate a complete Pod creation through ALL policies? (10-50ms)\n\nReal-world example:\n• When you create a Deployment, it might trigger 5 different policy rules\n• Each rule takes 2-5ms (Policy Rule Latency)\n• But the complete request takes 15ms (Admission Request Latency)\n• The difference includes networking, coordination, and processing overhead\n\nHow this query works:\n• Groups results by resource type (Pod, Deployment), operation (create, update, delete), and outcome (allowed/denied)\n• Shows the end-to-end user experience - how long developers wait for their kubectl commands\n• Uses 95th percentile to reveal realistic worst-case performance, not just averages\n\nThis metric represents the actual user experience when interacting with your Kubernetes cluster through Kyverno policies.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          },
          "custom": {
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 0,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "hideFrom": {
              "legend": false,
              "tooltip": false,
              "viz": false
            },
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 3,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": {
              "type": "linear"
            },
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "spanNulls": true,
            "stacking": {
              "group": "A",
              "mode": "none"
            },
            "thresholdsStyle": {
              "mode": "off"
            }
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 80
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 8
      },
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [],
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "single",
          "sort": "none"
